{"tid":1995100,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[港台電視] 大自然大不同 逢星期日 2030-2100","createTime":"2020-04-30T04:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T12:56:14.000Z","uid":30,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b3c52e80d0271bb492457c0000a4d55b7c11e3a2","tid":1995100,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T04:00:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">約定你，5月3日夜晚八點半，港台電視31！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ud90eH9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUd90eH9.jpg&h=51b0c014&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n生物多樣性在大自然中是生死攸關的，<br />\n因為在每一個生態系統中不同的物種都連在一起，互相倚靠。<br />\n一連六集紀錄片大自然大不同，嘗試用生動有趣的手法，<br />\n去紀錄香港不同物種，怎様去適應，去生存。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/biodiversityinhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2F&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=fb1a7037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/biodiversityinhk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/biodiversityinhk/videos/3760187454023398/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Fvideos%2F3760187454023398%2F&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=6bc58c22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/biodiversityinhk/videos/3760187454023398/</a><br />\n<br />\n今個夏天，我哋為你帶來不一樣嘅節目。過去一年，我哋嘅導演攀山涉水，拍低同我哋一齊共享呢個香港嘅六種動物嘅生活。想睇吓你以往無細望嘅大自然世界，記得留意我哋就快出街嘅節目《大自然大不同》啦！"},{"pid":"c4d94331190c97ad18e7cdbb3e6d92eb9a473865","tid":1995100,"uid":30,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T04:02:53.000Z","msg":"蜂情萬種<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/biodiversityinhk/originals/mfile_8895_678302_10_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8895_678302_10_l.jpg&h=ab52c67b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/biodiversityinhk/originals/mfile_8895_678302_7_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8895_678302_7_l.jpg&h=9a42327f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/biodiversityinhk/originals/mfile_8895_678302_5_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8895_678302_5_l.jpg&h=9eb7e242&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/biodiversityinhk/originals/mfile_8895_678302_4_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8895_678302_4_l.jpg&h=7175897c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港有數百個蜂類品種，蜂類在生態系統裡極為重要。我們會拜訪勤勞、兇猛和狡猾的蜂類，觀察牠們複雜的生活方式和獨特的社會結構。我們將會看到木蜂孜孜不倦地採集花蜜、胡蜂蜂后建立族群、黃腳胡蜂屠殺蜜蜂等，探討牠們如何各出奇謀適應不同的生境。"},{"pid":"5676be3ee70783ee04a4c6ca3aaa449ee85e5c5c","tid":1995100,"uid":121275,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T15:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WxxtAdm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxxtAdm.jpg&h=a02ba54b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8750e134af6e100ba742e0eb258926bd76b25d3","tid":1995100,"uid":12991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:47:51.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1107c5e5ea3d817de63e41fab92ac7c547d04ecb","tid":1995100,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T23:02:12.000Z","msg":"《大自然大不同》第一集《蜂情萬種》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/biodiversityinhk/videos/558590401709841/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Fvideos%2F558590401709841%2F&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=a43d917a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/biodiversityinhk/videos/558590401709841/</a><br />\n<br />\n「嗡嗡嗡，嗡嗡嗡，我是一隻小蜜蜂&hellip;」呢句歌詞，相信都係大家嘅集體回憶。<br />\n不過其實蜜蜂只係成個蜂類家族中小小一部分，而成個大家族入面有好多你平時唔覺的品種，單單係香港，就已經有幾百種。<br />\n而《大自然大不同》打頭炮嘅，正正係香港蜂類！<br />\n想知道我哋跟拍咗咩蜂類？記住留意5月3日呢個大日子，然後準時8點半去港台電視31收睇 Daphne Wong - Photographer &amp; Filmmaker 製作嘅《蜂情萬種》"},{"pid":"1de6527d5229c4c590620f596a6b25e31c1c7ce7","tid":1995100,"uid":30,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T00:43:30.000Z","msg":"Daphne Wong<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/daphnewongphoto/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdaphnewongphoto%2F&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=66a749ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/daphnewongphoto/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/29101549_561595734216330_2228578939855437824_o.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_sid=85a577&amp;_nc_ohc=jPWHP7m_1lIAX-NpTHS&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=cde68bbf11da22f832b281a18b02a49a&amp;oe=5ED533C4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F29101549_561595734216330_2228578939855437824_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_sid%3D85a577%26_nc_ohc%3DjPWHP7m_1lIAX-NpTHS%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3Dcde68bbf11da22f832b281a18b02a49a%26oe%3D5ED533C4&h=a1d19a52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54215c0ac2c2f2d8aca026bcf7353679a79743b5","tid":1995100,"uid":49359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T02:03:37.000Z","msg":"睇廣告