ityinhk/videos/337328730579121/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Fvideos%2F337328730579121%2F&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=a8e2bc1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/biodiversityinhk/videos/337328730579121/</a><br />\n<br />\n講起兩棲類，大家第一樣諗起嘅，相信都會係青蛙。<br />\n細細個睇教科書都會知道，青蛙係由卵孵化成蝌蚪，再長大成蛙，不過原來每種蛙類成個配對過程都會有啲唔同，有咩唔同？咁就要留意吓我哋嚟緊個集紀錄片了！<br />\n除咗青蛙，我哋重會介紹蠑螈。香港唯一一種本土蠑螈叫香港瘰螈。佢外表得得意意，有「香港」兩個字都已經值得你哋留意啦！<br />\n想睇吓佢哋兩種物種嘅愛情故事？咁就記得5月10日準時8點半去港台電視31收睇《兩棲大不同》啦！<br />\n<br />\n#香港製造 #自家製作 #本土生態紀錄片 #支持吓啦 #大自然大不同 #生物多樣性 #5月10號夜晚8點半 #31台 #原來香港真係咁靚 #香港瘰螈 #聽到有香港兩個字都想睇啦 #青蛙下蛋 #唔係講緊嘢食呀"},{"pid":"dc4f267f8959a49a605dc5c2734515bf9fa2a8a7","tid":1995100,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:19:52.000Z","msg":"d屎有香港既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25baf9abc5f7e3d05c0ef8cd3a22ff1e06a3d42b","tid":1995100,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:20:22.000Z","msg":"兩棲大不同    10/05/2020<br />\n<br />\n繁衍下一代是不同物種的天職，而大部分兩棲動物的繁殖仍然離不開淡水棲息地，可能我們有種錯覺是牠們在水產完卵就是，其實不同的蛙類、蠑螈為傳宗接代，盡顯本領。<br />\n沼蛙用又快又多的交配策略，班腿泛樹蛙用泡泡包著卵子懸掛起來，而香港瘰螈把卵子產在石菖蒲葉子之間，使其得到保護。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/biodiversityinhk/originals/mfile_8895_679505_10_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8895_679505_10_l.jpg&h=5ab38540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/biodiversityinhk/originals/mfile_8895_679505_3_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8895_679505_3_l.jpg&h=a608ebd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/biodiversityinhk/originals/mfile_8895_679505_5_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8895_679505_5_l.jpg&h=ab169b93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/biodiversityinhk/originals/mfile_8895_679505_4_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8895_679505_4_l.jpg&h=44d4f0ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4018eadc1c697e54d08fd298879e27a138465c5b","tid":1995100,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:30:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944780434d9e0f13faffe3f5d3e78ca613a21d4e","tid":1995100,"uid":345819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:34:50.000Z","msg":"今晚schedule <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2030-2100 大自然大不同RTHK31<br />\n2030-2130 恐怖醫學 viutv<br />\n2130-2230 空間改造王 開電視<br />\n2130-2200 運輸背後 RTHK31"},{"pid":"93a3008ee3494490c058ca58c378ef3d940182f2","tid":1995100,"uid":345819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:39:23.000Z","msg":"排卵啲聲係live record定effect嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d129df4ec7f19493aa0e0bdc44403cb5902e34ef","tid":1995100,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:40:51.000Z","msg":"小孩騎大車"},{"pid":"795699da7acd7b4f9293dd359176d45d6f08e154","tid":1995100,"uid":30294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93a3008ee3494490c058ca58c378ef3d940182f2","tid":1995100,"uid":345819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:39:23.000Z","msg":"排卵啲聲係live record定effect嚟<img src=\"