/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3306abc7f4efc5414402a5bd9153c16272537c","tid":1995100,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T02:06:41.000Z","msg":"之前幾集攀過山涉過水，但睇到嘅風景都係平日行山去海灘都可能睇到，覺得唔夠特別？咁要留意聽晚嘅《大自然大不同》～～因為今集要潛入水底！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHK.HK/videos/901039396987809/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHK.HK%2Fvideos%2F901039396987809%2F&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=a7ca338b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHK.HK/videos/901039396987809/</a><br />\n講起珊瑚，大家可能都會諗起澳洲大堡礁，又或者近年潛水熱點台灣蘭嶼，不過其實香港嘅海底世界，同樣有好靚嘅珊瑚㗎！除咗珊瑚，海底世界仲有好多海洋生物，唔係潛開水嘅我哋，相信平時都唔會見過呢一道風景。<br />\n<br />\n對海洋世界好奇嘅話，睇住預告片過吓癮先啦！然後記住留意，今個星期日（5月31日） 8:30pm #港台電視31 播放嘅第五集《大自然大不同》&mdash;&mdash;《潛覓珊瑚》。<br />\n<br />\n#香港製造 #自家製作 #本土生態紀錄片 #支持吓啦 #大自然大不同 #生物多樣性 #潛覓珊瑚 #珊瑚 #重有其他海洋生物 #海參<br />\n#幫手forward出去比多啲人知啦 #5月31號夜晚8點半 #31台<br />\n#唔駛擔心 #睇唔到都有重溫嘅"},{"pid":"18132217ee3735d17b11d03c2c4a551ad0fe50bc","tid":1995100,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T02:09:21.000Z","msg":"大自然大不同 - 潛覓珊瑚<br />\n<br />\n香港水域發現了84種石珊瑚，比加勒比海的種類更加多。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/biodiversityinhk/originals/mfile_8895_683156_3_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8895_683156_3_l.jpg&h=3cf01f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/biodiversityinhk/originals/mfile_8895_683156_9_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8895_683156_9_l.jpg&h=2bd28fc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/biodiversityinhk/originals/mfile_8895_683156_8_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8895_683156_8_l.jpg&h=c410e4f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/biodiversityinhk/originals/mfile_8895_683156_4_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8895_683156_4_l.jpg&h=de2c0479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/biodiversityinhk/originals/mfile_8895_683156_2_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8895_683156_2_l.jpg&h=d332743e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/biodiversityinhk/originals/mfile_8895_683156_10_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8895_683156_10_l.jpg&h=db976b79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n珊瑚究竟是動物，還是植物？珊瑚會用觸手覓食、互相攻擊，還懂得「生蛋」繁殖？<br />\n<br />\n珊瑚為各種海洋生物提供了棲息的場所，一間間「房屋」又有哪些住客？是喜歡背著海葵到處走的寄居蟹，是身穿堅硬盔甲的琵琶蝦，還是身體會變色的偽裝高手「青蛙魚」？"},{"pid":"864ca34e7f6aa461382c02baef5d8ebc0221da69","tid":1995100,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T02:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3825c002a7417b2fbddceaba47b836a077330cf","tid":1995100,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T02:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b15695740e29eeb44a3c2238fb56c89648dba2f","tid":1995100,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:51:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"h