sode/683230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Fepisode%2F683230&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=10848459\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/biodiversityinhk/episode/683230</a><br />\n<br />\n大自然大不同    去留。鳥斷<br />\n不同的鳥類因各種原因以香港為家或暫棲之所，展示大自然恆常流動、生生不息的一面。<br />\n香港戰後樹林重新茂盛，林鳥品種日益繁多。我們攀山涉水觀察林鳥各種有趣行為。而以涉禽為例，留鳥與渡冬候鳥發展出不同的生存之道蔚為壯觀。今天，鳥類的行為不免受人類影響，在城市中例子更明顯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/biodiversityinhk/originals/mfile_8895_683230_10_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8895_683230_10_l.jpg&h=92cd956b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/biodiversityinhk/originals/mfile_8895_683230_1_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8895_683230_1_l.jpg&h=0bbc90db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/biodiversityinhk/originals/mfile_8895_683230_8_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8895_683230_8_l.jpg&h=f7a9bb11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/biodiversityinhk/originals/mfile_8895_683230_7_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fbiodiversityinhk%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8895_683230_7_l.jpg&h=06a2e09c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/biodiversityinhk/originals/mfile_8895_683230_6_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt